author: cnbc.com
title: Deere & Company Announces Quarterly Dividend
text:
MOLINE, Ill., Feb. 28, 2018 /PRNewswire/ -- The Deere & Company (NYSE: DE) Board of Directors declared a regular quarterly dividend of $.60 per share on common stock, payable May 1, 2018, to stockholders of record on March 29, 2018.
